data.title: Bobby Gazak - Football

data.text:
2014: Named to the PFL Academic Honor Roll…Redshirted the 2014 season…

2013: Played in three games on the defensive line…Made four tackles for the season, three solo…Added a quarterback hurry…Made two tackles in a win at Davidson…Added tackles against Charlotte and UVA-Wise…

2012: Notched 19 tackles, making 14 assisted and five solo stops…Added 1.0 sack for an eight yard loss and a pass breakup for the season…Played in 10 games as a freshman, starting six contests…Registered a season-high seven tackles, including a sack against Valparaiso…Made four tackles against Davidson…Made two tackles against Old Dominion, Drake and San Diego…Earned a letter…
